data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Youngs Englewood area of NW Oklahoma City, this recently renovated 4-plex offers a blend of convenience and contemporary living. Each of its four units boasts 2 spacious bedrooms and a modern bathroom, ensuring comfort for its residents. With fresh paint, sleek laminate flooring, and elegant granite countertops, these units exude a fresh and modern ambiance. Central heat and air ensure year-round comfort, while the inclusion of essential appliances like a stove and refrigerator make for a hassle-free move-in. Located just a brisk 10-minute drive from downtown, residents can enjoy easy access to city amenities while retreating to their tranquil neighborhood. Disclosure: Agent is related to the seller. Photos will be added 9/10.
